Compilation:

While in A1/ directory, run the following command to compile the program:
	$ premake4 gmake
	$ make
	run the program by:
	$ ./A1

No change was made to the default premake4/make combination.
The program was compiled an run on lab machine gl30.

Manual:

There are two addtional files:
	Cell.cpp
	Cell.hpp
There are some addtional features:
	1) Use the indicator colour slider to change its colour to your liking.
	2) Hold the A key will turn the current active bar to white to better indicate
           your position.
	3) You can choose to reset the current cell by clicking on the Reset
           Current Cell button or hold shift and then press R.
